</head><body><table border=0 align=center width=80%><tr><td class=textbody><center><h1> Insignia Earring of Veracity</h1><br>by Gemdiver</center><br><div align="center">
  <center>
  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="573" id="AutoNumber1">
    <tr>
      <td width="573">
  <p align="center">This is the first of the Seru earring quests.</p>

  <hr noshade>

      </div>

  <p align="left">Obtain four bixie crunchies. These can be bought in the bazaar 
  or you can bake them without too much skill.</p>
  <p align="left">Also obtain some dawnshroud cider from the merchant in Sanctus 
  Seru, located around +825, -600.</p>
  <p align="left">Give the cider to Legionnaire Dalni in the Netherbian Lair. 
  This causes Bregun Derov to spawn inside the caves located in the same zone. 
  Give him the four crunchies and he will give you a Bixie Charm. </p>
  <p align="left">Take the charm to Torsten Reidan in Sanctus Seru (-1000, -500) 
  and he will give you a letter.</p>
  <p align="left">Head back to Netherbian Lair and get the letter to Bregun, he 
  will give you back a note.</p>
  <p align="left">Finally take this note back to Torsten in Sanctus Seru, and he 
  will give you an Insignia Earring.</p>

